==Korean==
'''유행성 이하선염''' ''yu-haeng-seong i-ha-seon-yeom''
:also written as one word: '''유행성이하선염'''
===Noun===
#[[mumps]]; any infectious inflammation of the [[parotid gland]]s
===Etymology===
From hanja [[流行性耳下腺炎]], made up of [[流行性]], "infectious" + [[耳下腺]], "parotid gland" + [[炎]], "inflammation".
